snippet: D. A. Points came back from a long rain delay and made four pars Sunday, the last one giving him a one-shot victory in the Houston Open and a trip to the Masters.
abstract: D A Points earns one-shot victory in Houston Open golf tournament and trip to the Masters.
lead_paragraph: D. A. Points came back from a long rain delay and made four pars Sunday, the last one giving him a one-shot victory in the Houston Open and a trip to the Masters.
